      <div xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364">
        <head xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Hd1e99" type="question-title">De aequitate</head>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e102">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e112" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e104">Gregorius, in <title>Registro</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e112">Ita vos in ea, quae Deum offendunt, et ad
              iracundiam provocant, districtos ac sollicitos exhibete, ut ad aliorum emendationem et
              vindicta culpabilem feriat, et innocentem falsa opinio non affligat.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e117">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e127" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e119">Gregorius, in <title>Registro</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e127">Manifesta peccata non sunt occulta correctione
              purganda, sed palam sunt arguendi, qui palam nocent: ut dum aperta objurgatione
              sanantur, hi qui eos imitando deliquerant, corrigantur.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e132">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e142" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e134">Gregorius, in <title>Registro</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e142">Cum increpare delinquentes noluerit, eos
              proculdubio pastor occidit. Hac ergo consideratione compulsus, velis, nolis, locuturus
              sum: quia omni virtute aut te cupio salvari, aut de tua morte me eripi.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e147">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e157" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e149">Gregorius, in <title>Registro</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e157">Sicut obstinati esse humilibus non debemus, ita
              districti esse superbis debemus.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e163">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e173" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e165">Gregorius, in <title>Registro</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e173">Sicut perseveranti culpae debetur jure vindicta,
              ita resipiscentibus est venia concedenda.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e178">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e188" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e180">Gregorius, in <title>Registro</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e188">Boni te dulcem, pravi sentiant correctorem. In
              qua videlicet correctione hunc esse ordinem noveris observandum, ut personam diligas,
              et vitia persequaris: ne si aliter agere fortasse volueris, transeat in crudelitatem
              correctio, et perdas quos emendare desideras.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e193">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e203" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e195">Gregorius, in <title>Registro</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e203">Justitiae et rationis ordo suadet, ut qui sua a
              successoribus desiderat mandata servari, praedecessoris sui proculdubio voluntatem et
              statuta custodiat.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e208">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e218" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e210">Gregorius, in <title>Registro</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e218">Sicut in his, qui per ignorantiam fecerunt,
              culpa aliquatenus toleranda est; ita in his fortiter insequenda, qui non metuunt
              sciendo peccare.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e223">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e233" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e225">Gregorius, in <title>Registro</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e233">Effectum justa postulantibus indulgere, et vigor
              aequitatis, et ordo exigit rationis, praesertim quando petentium voluntatem, et pietas
              adjuvat, et veritas non relinquit.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e238">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e248" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e240">Gregorius, in <title>Registro</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e248">Sicut rationi contraria procul est abjicienda
              petitio; ita in his, quae bene desiderantur, effectum non convenit negare.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e254">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e264" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e256">Gregorius, in <title>Registro</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e264">Minorem major praecedit, sicut honore, ita et
              crimine: et quem major sequitur culpa, majori plectatur vindicta, et sic postea
              poenitentia credatur esse fructuosa.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e269">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e279" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e271">Gregorius, in <title>Registro</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e279">Sicut laudabile, discretumque est, reverentiam
              et honorem debitum exhibere prioribus, ita rectitudinis et Dei timoris est, si qua in
              eis correctione indigent, nulla dissimulatione postponere: ne totum, quod absit,
              incipiat corpus invadere, si languor non fuerit curatus in capite.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e284">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e294" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e286">Gregorius, in <title>Registro</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e294">Manifesti excessus canonica semper moderatione
              premendi sunt: ut una res, et praeteritorum correctio, et esse regula possit
              futurorum.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e299">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e309" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e301">Gregorius, in <title>Registro</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e309">Quoties contra ecclesiasticam quid gestum
              dicitur disciplinam, ne nos ante Deum culpa ex dissimulatione redarguat, irrequisitum
              hoc relinquere non audemus.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e314">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e324" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e316">Gregorius, in <title>Registro</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e324">Sicut Ecclesia proprias res amittere non debet,
              ita eam rapacitatis ardore alienas invadere non oportet.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e329">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e339" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e331">Gregorius, in <title>Registro</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e339">Jurgantium controversias celeri sententia
              terminare, et aequitati proculdubio convenit, et vigori.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e345">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e355" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e347">Gregorius, in <title>Registro</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e355">Sicut ab aliis nostra exigimus, ita singulis sua
              jura servemus.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e360">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e370" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e362">Gregorius, in <title>Moralibus</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e370">Majora crimina, et tarde credenda sunt, cum
              audiuntur, et citius punienda sunt, cum veraciter agnoscuntur.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e375">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e385" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e377">Gregorius, in <title>Moralibus</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e385">Superiores cum per disciplinam alios feriunt,
              sic alienam infirmitatem debent percutere, ut etiam ad suam noverint oculos
              revocare.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e390">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e400" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e392">Gregorius, in <title>Pastorali</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e400">Aliquando subjectorum vitia prudenter
              dissimulanda sunt, sed quia dissimulantur, indicanda; aliquando etiam aperte cognita,
              mature toleranda; aliquando vero subtiliter et occulte perscrutanda, aliquando leniter
              arguenda; aliquando et vehementer increpanda.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e405">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e415" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e407">Ambrosius, in <title>Epistola</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e415">Hostem ferire, victoria est; reum, aequitas;
              innocentem, homicidium.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e420">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e430" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e422">Augustinus, <title>de Civitate Dei</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e430" source="http://scta.info/resource/adcd-l19-d1e3127">Melior est animi aequitas, quam
              corporis sanitas.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e436">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e446" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e438">Augustinus, <title>de Unico baptismate</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e446">Hoc justum est, ut cum mala hominum reprobamus,
              quaecumque in illis bona Dei reperimus, approbemus.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e451">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e461" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e453">Augustinus, <title>de Unico baptismate</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e461">Veritate manente, quod vitiosum, quod pravum,
              quod falsum in unoquoque fuerit, curemus, corrigamus, emendemus, aut si non possumus,
              detestatum damnatumque vitemus.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e466">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e476" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e468">Augustinus, <title>de Ovibus</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e476">Disciplina exerceatur, judicium non
              praecipitetur.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e481">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e491" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e483">Joannes Chrysostomus, <title>super Joannem</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e491">Sive inops, sive dives fuerit quis, non personas
              attendamus, sed res scrutemur.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e496">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e506" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e498">Bernardus, in <title>Epistola</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e506">Si quis susurro in populo diaboli sibi assumens
              vicem, jurgia seminare, et pacem turbare velle reperiatur, quemadmodum ille discordiae
              semper est amator et auctor; huic rigidae censurae remedio citius obvietur, eo quippe
              pessimae, quo intimae pesti.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e511">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e521" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e513">Bernardus, in <title>Epistola</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e521">Malum si comprimas tuum, reputabitur tibi ad
              gloriam; si alienum, ad justitiam.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-d1e527">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e537" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Rd1e529">Bernardus, in <title>Epistola</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e46364-Qd1e537">Melius est ut pereat unus, quam unitas.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
      </div>
